-- Adriatic Town of Sibenik in Line for Development Bank Water Loan
-- B y   R a n d a l l   H a c k l e y
-- 2013-10-11T10:51:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-10-11/adriatic-town-of-sibenik-in-line-for-development-bank-water-loan.html
The Adriatic coastal town of Sibenik
is in line for a European Bank for Reconstruction and
Development loan for water utility works to modernize and
enlarge pumping stations, pipes and the wastewater network.  Vodovod i Odvodnja d.o.o. plans to use 10 million euros
($13.6 million) of proceeds from the development bank to finance
the project construction works in the Croatian town, the EBRD
said yesterday on its website.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Randall Hackley in London at 
